review:
I visited with concerns about a couple of poorly done Root Canal Treatments (RCTs) and a subpar crown job on my front teeth. review:
I would like to thank team Dentpark for their amazing work and friendly staff. 
I have been to Dentpark since in 2020 having to get done a root canal on my wisdom tooth and yet here I am back again in  India' 2023 for yet another set of filling,  a root canal and Dental Bridge. Thank you to the doctor who worked on it Dr. Malick, Dr. Mushtaq and Dr. Pooja, please do keep up the amazing working you guys are doing and I will be back one day.
I would highly recommend Dentpark because of the friendly staff,  service, AMAZING work and I must admit this place is very hygienic.
